name: yuki-promote-checker
description: used to auto create promote checking experiments

scripts.start: rm -rf ./dist && tsc && mkdir -p ./dist/src/internal && cp src/internal/createPrompt.js ./dist/src/internal/createPrompt.js && mkdir -p ./dist/data && cp ./data/words.csv ./dist/data && node dist/src/index.js
scripts.start-sd: rm -rf ./dist && tsc && mkdir -p ./dist/src/internal && cp src/internal/createPrompt.js ./dist/src/internal/createPrompt.js && mkdir -p ./dist/data && cp ./data/words.csv ./dist/data && node dist/src/runStableDiffusion.js
scripts.start-server: rm -rf ./dist && tsc && mkdir -p ./dist/src/internal && cp src/internal/createPrompt.js ./dist/src/internal/createPrompt.js && mkdir -p ./dist/data && cp ./data/words.csv ./dist/data && node dist/src/server/index.js
